PEOPLE 
Michael A. Carpenter, president and chief executive of Kidder, Peabody &amp; 
Co., New York, was elected to the additional post of chairman. Carpenter 
succeeds Silas S. Cathcart, who retired in January. Two Kidder executives were 
elected to the board: Scott C. Newquist, managing director and head of Kidder's 
investment banking group, and Richard W. O'Donnell, chief financial and 
administrative officer. 
